{"tid":2238573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【落選男友】10日前否認分手！落選港姐「狂野空姐」廖慧儀男友自爆被狠飛：點解要咁對我？","createTime":"2020-10-11T08:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T09:41:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0639c16b027a67111f0ae79cc8b55aed42d5ae","tid":2238573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/10-日前否認分手廖慧儀男友自爆被狠飛點解要咁對我-050910753.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F10-%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B%E5%BB%96%E6%85%A7%E5%84%80%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E8%A2%AB%E7%8B%A0%E9%A3%9B%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E5%92%81%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%91-050910753.html&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=b390a979\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/10-日前否認分手廖慧儀男友自爆被狠飛點解要咁對我-050910753.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KZpAEGYbHBoTlEqEIOLZ5w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/d7ae2b40-0b7f-11eb-bfaf-05bc874abf9d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKZpAEGYbHBoTlEqEIOLZ5w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2Fd7ae2b40-0b7f-11eb-bfaf-05bc874abf9d&h=15125be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「狂野空姐」之稱嘅落選港姐廖慧儀是非多多，本身有圈外男友Sam嘅佢，早前被指撻着無綫節目《#後生仔傾吓偈》嘅23歲孔德賢（Danny），Sam嬲到喺社交網公開「警告」Danny唔好再搵自己女友。廖慧儀當日接受東網訪問時表示同男友仲拍緊拖，對方只係飲醉咗，而Sam就話對女朋友百分百信任，懷疑兩人拍拖係自己問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wvfpSLVo0gqOMVPguG3AGg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9Nzgw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/fb4cd240-0b7f-11eb-94e7-10750d75cb7b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwvfpSLVo0gqOMVPguG3AGg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9Nzgw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2Ffb4cd240-0b7f-11eb-94e7-10750d75cb7b&h=0d5aa7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知事隔10日，Sam今日凌晨突然喺社交網發文自爆被狠飛：「同你一齊呢一年半，大大小小傷心嘅事我都陪你經歷過，喺你有低潮困難嘅時候，我從來冇離開過你身邊，而點會（解）你要咁樣對我，去報答我一年半對你嘅所有付出？我一直當你係一家人，點解要選擇因為一啲小問題而突然狠心離開我，係咪因為入咗娛樂圈擴闊咗眼界，回頭看所有嘢覺得我甚麼都不是？」佢又隨文附上一張兩人互咬食物甜蜜照，不過之後佢已將Post刪走！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eiimafmDl2_sIMucxYY.5w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9Nzgw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/21cca030-0b80-11eb-bfdf-06efca0ee83b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FeiimafmDl2_sIMucxYY.5w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9Nzgw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F21cca030-0b80-11eb-bfdf-06efca0ee83b&h=6b3e9518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另邊廂，廖慧儀尋晚就上載單人瑜伽照，尋日仲同男女朋友去行山，露出美甜笑容，心情似乎相當好！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/v9KH8.o2iJHtaQXhT0iVeg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9OTQ4/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/4160e280-0b80-11eb-b7bf-0fb4471a2f02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fv9KH8.o2iJHtaQXhT0iVeg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9OTQ4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F4160e280-0b80-11eb-b7bf-0fb4471a2f02&h=4ad71e1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58c79fa2baa1d64af90d24f6e4f7b4f210b41b95","tid":2238573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"屌, 開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330b5ccf3664b6df2fc86af3f2fc5c16562e6cb0","tid":2238573,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike"